{"tid":1948914,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"29/3 - 辣招期都唔等？ 嘉湖山莊業主減價急讓　輸使費沽貨離場","createTime":"2020-03-29T09:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T16:46:11.000Z","uid":62935,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4e455f6ae17a62a65c96a5b039658e236a309fb5","tid":1948914,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200329/mobile/bkn-20200329124323687-0329_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200329%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200329124323687-0329_00842_001.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=44880640\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200329/mobile/bkn-20200329124323687-0329_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓市走勢持續向下，市場再錄業主損手個案，中原馬斯力表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊美湖居5座中層H室，實用面積540方呎，三房間隔，以531萬港元售出，呎價僅9,833元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，原業主於2017年6月以520萬元買入單位，由於需要資金周轉，故等不及今年6月屆滿3年辣招期，就要急讓單位。</span></span>上址原先以610萬元包額外印花稅放售，最後以上述價錢易手，但相關稅項則由買方負責，即買家實際支付約584多萬元入市。而業主持貨不足3年，帳面只獲利11萬元，扣除代理佣金等開支難免蝕使費離場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6 月就捱到辣招禁售完，都等唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始有 生意撚 / 股票撚 撲水潮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de5fc9847ac2284b74f40fbc4ec340069cbc6f6","tid":1948914,"uid":289946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"諗起呢度有巴打580買2房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf1a39b7425c4e9acb0aad7041edfeccf7e0dea","tid":1948914,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e455f6ae17a62a65c96a5b039658e236a309fb5","tid":1948914,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200329/mobile/bkn-2020032912432368